Description: Point of Sale (POS) system
 easyPOS is a comprehensive Point of Sale system built with Qt6.
 It provides features for sales management, inventory control,
 employee management, reporting, and more.
 .
 Features:
  - Sales management and checkout
  - Inventory and stock management
  - Employee and role management
  - Production and recipe management
  - Comprehensive reporting system
  - Multi-language support (Russian, English)

